# Project Overview

This is the **Covenant AI Consulting** monorepo — a workflow consulting business that uses AI-powered screen capture analysis to identify and implement automation opportunities for businesses.

## Repository Structure

| Package | Path | Stack | Purpose |
|---------|------|-------|---------|
| Marketing Site | `marketing-site/` | Next.js, React, TypeScript, Tailwind | covenantai.consulting |
| Client Portal | `client-portal/` | FastAPI (MVP) → Next.js | Audit results and engagement tracking |
| Capture Agent | `capture-agent/` | Electron, Node.js | Desktop screen capture + activity logger |
| Analysis Engine | `analysis-engine/` | Python 3.12, Claude API | Workflow pattern detection pipeline |
| Docs | `docs/` | Markdown | Case studies, templates |

## Key Conventions

- All secrets live in `.env` files (gitignored). Never commit credentials.
- The marketing site shares design DNA with Covenant Sites (navy/gold palette).
- The analysis engine uses Claude API for vision (screen OCR) and text (pattern synthesis).
- The capture agent requires explicit employee consent and has built-in privacy controls.
- This project is related to but independent from the Covenant Sites / Enoch GraceWeb repo.
